 'Hạn': ['no bars', 'I’m not going to sugarcoat it: this is the star at its weakest. Expect its problems way more than its gifts. So in this part of your life — go slow, double-check everything, and please don’t gamble here. Careful and humble wins this one.'],
 'Hãm': ['no bars', 'I’m not going to sugarcoat it: this is the star at its weakest. Expect its problems way more than its gifts. So in this part of your life — go slow, double-check everything, and please don’t gamble here. Careful and humble wins this one.']
